      "parameters": {
        "description": "Read & filter OVH emails from your mailbox. Optional filters: seen (true=read, false=unread), from, subject, searchText (body), flagged, answered, since/before (YYYY-MM-DD), mailbox, limit (default 50). For marking: set action=mark with emailUid and markAsRead/markFlagged/markDeleted.",
